newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 2,163 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 2,163 contracts.

text.p: Chicago Board of Trade said its Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totaled 2,163 contracts compared with 6,220 overnight Sunday.
There were 360 wheat, 1,033 corn, 555 soybean, 19 soymeal, 12 soyoil, five oat, three corn calls, 173 corn puts and three soybean calls traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was 1-3/4 to 4-1/4 cents lower, corn was 2-1/2 to three cents lower and soybeans were 4-1/2 to 8-3/4 cents lower.
